A '''mutated contraction''' is a [[etymology|etymological]] phenomenon when a new word or [[slang]] term develops when a longer word is shortened and slightly altered. Many mutated contractions are considered offensive and disrespectful. 

===Examples of Mutated Contractions===

* Newfie, for Newfoundlander
* Fundie, for Fundamentalist, considered derogatory
* Packie, for Pakistani, considered a racial slur